desc: Ewan Cameron of Timber Grooves makes a range of custom timber furniture, signs and art from his workshop in Vasse, Western Australia. He collaborates with CAST Designs on timber and concrete tables, photographer Anj Semark on art and balance boards, and Skender Designs to make steel and timber furniture.

layout.text: A love of designing and making unique furniture sparked Ewan Cameron's Timber Grooves journey.
